{"tid":2111743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"ISIS新娘批准入境英國上訴英國citizenship","createTime":"2020-07-16T18:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T19:38:58.000Z","uid":253723,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"310187363befa70f012b106bcbd3f1bed5ec479f","tid":2111743,"uid":253723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w9bjZO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w9bjZO.jpg&h=ed7048a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n哩條女英國出世 2015年自願離開英國加入ISIS恐怖組織被英國revoke citizenship<br />\n<br />\n今日英國court of appeal 批准佢入境英國上訴<br />\n仲要英國出錢帶佢返英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-53427197\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-53427197&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFac5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=7bd47102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-53427197</a>"},{"pid":"a01df6eaf86a62df76bbf581c3f65e5891139b47","tid":2111743,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:45:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MS9WEs1HtQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMS9WEs1HtQk&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFac5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=55085f1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MS9WEs1HtQk</a>"},{"pid":"00ae55c147854e7a2571d7f1c94c833fdee167d7","tid":2111743,"uid":166405,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:46:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母英國<br />\nIsis就貼錢比佢黎<br />\n香港人就搞咁撚多野"},{"pid":"b4c072f06d21bc2362bf285501ccc961eadd42cd","tid":2111743,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T18:48:58.000Z","msg":"英國法治已死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3d4d9a1e956f35b1060aa7426e5bef0fd3b154","tid":2111743,"uid":253723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"re